WEBVTT

00:00:00.719 --> 00:00:03.612
Everyone needs a coach.

00:00:03.612 --> 00:00:06.713
It doesn't matter whether you're a basketball player,

00:00:06.713 --> 00:00:09.991
a tennis player, a gymnast

00:00:09.991 --> 00:00:12.212
or a bridge player.

00:00:12.212 --> 00:00:14.701
(Laughter)

00:00:14.701 --> 00:00:17.160
My bridge coach, Sharon Osberg,

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:19.415
says there are more pictures of the back of her head

00:00:19.415 --> 00:00:22.932
than anyone else's in the world. (Laughter)

00:00:22.932 --> 00:00:26.594
Sorry, Sharon. Here you go.

00:00:26.594 --> 00:00:30.185
We all need people who will give us feedback.